ŽIN FOND MEMORY OF
JOHN CATER, ACTOR, LONDONER, FATHER & GRANDFATHER
17.1.1932 - 21.3.2009
Descended from generations of florists who daily used Old Covent Garden Market.
Married in this church 11.11.1963"ė
ąRose (25.10.1916 - 24.12.2004) and Norman Winter (22.12.1910-26.11.1999)
Wonderful Mum and Dad, Nanny and Grandad. A Lifetime of Happy Memories in this Beautiful and Peaceful Park.
Come rest a while with us"ė
